{"title":"The World-Changing Impact of Vaccines","link":"https://kottke.org/24/11/the-world-changing-impact-of-vaccines","date":1732205429000,"content":"\n        <p>Back in 2015, Tynan DeBold and Dov Friedman <a href=\"https://graphics.wsj.com/infectious-diseases-and-vaccines/\">created a series of graphics for the WSJ showing the impact of the introduction of vaccines in the US</a>. Hereâ€™s the infographic for measles:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-01.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-01.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-01.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1099\" height=\"724\" alt=\"infographic showing the quick decline in the number of infected people after the introduction of the measles vaccine\" /></p>\n\n<p>And for polio:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-02.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-02.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/vax-graphs-02.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1098\" height=\"722\" alt=\"infographic showing the quick decline in the number of infected people after the introduction of the polio vaccine\" /></p>\n\n<p>Vaccines are in the running for the greatest human invention ever. You can <a href=\"https://graphics.wsj.com/infectious-diseases-and-vaccines/\">see the rest of the charts (for hepatitis A, mumps, pertussis, rubella, and smallpox) here</a>.</p>\n\n<p>See also <a href=\"https://www.vox.com/future-perfect/386215/trump-rfk-jr-vaccines-health-measles-chart\">The stunning success of vaccines in America, in one chart</a>.</p>\n\n        \n\n         <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <a href=\"http